</XX>
<CN>FRZ  France, EC.
    SEZ  Sweden, West Europe.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P3711  Motor Vehicles and Car Bodies.
    P3713  Truck and Bus Bodies.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>COMP  Strategic links.
</TP>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
