</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
INDUSTRIAL shares were generally firmer in low volume and the index closed
15 higher at 4,573. The overall index rose 3 to 3,418, while golds slipped 5
to 784 on a weaker bullion price. Barlow Rand lost 25 cents to R46 after
