FT  18 JAN 93 / World News in Brief: Storm hits California
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Los Angeles residents fought floods and mudslides after a fierce storm raked
southern California. Across the US-Mexican border in Tijuana, the storm
brought the death toll to 19 after two weeks of steady rain inundated the
city's shantytowns.
